quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,"Abo bangalindelanga kudibana naThi bathi: “Kwakutheni na ukuba kungathunyelwa iingelosi kuthi, okanye singayiboni iNkosi yethu?” Bona ngokwenene baye baba nenkukhumalo ngeziqu zabo baza badelela ngendelelo enkulu"
  25,22,"NgeMini abaya kuzibona ngayo iingelosi akuyi kubakho ndaba zivuyisayo ngaloo Mini kuzo izaphula-mthetho, yaye iingelosi ziya kuthi: “(Makubekho) isithintelo nokuvaleleka3.”"
  25,23,Ke kaloku Siya kukuthabatha oko bakwenzayo kuzizenzo zabo Size Sikwenze kube njengothuli kuphaphatheke (kuthi shwaka)
  25,24,"Amadlelane asePaladesi wona ngaloo Mini, aya kuba sentlalweni elungileyo nendawo elungileyo yokuphumla"
  25,25,"NgeMini apho izulu liya kwahlukaniswa livuleke linamafu, zize iingelosi zithunyelwe phantsi ngokulandelelana (kwazo ngokwezikhundla)"
  25,26,Ulongamelo lokwenene ngaloo Mini luya kuba lolukaSozinceba. Yaye kwabangakholwayo iya kuba yiMini yobunzima
  25,27,"NgeMini apho Umenzi wobubi aya kuluma izandla zakhe. Uya kuthi: “O, (Madoda) akwaba ndandizithabathele iNdlela (eNgqalileyo) noMthunywa"
  25,28,Yeha kum! Akwaba ndandingamthathanga ubanibani ukuba abe ngumhlobo wam osenyongweni
  25,29,Inene yena undilahlekisile kwinkumbulo (i’Kurân) emveni kokuba ifikile kum. Kwaye uShaytân ngumtyesheli womntu ngeyure yokuxakeka
  25,30,"Ke yena uMthunywa wathi: “Nkosi yethu! Inene, abantu bam bayityeshele le ‘Kur’ân"
  25,31,Ke kaloku Senzele umProfeti ngamnye utshaba oluphuma phakathi kwezaphula-mthetho. Kodwa Yanele iNkosi yakho iyodwa ukuba ibe nguMncedi
  25,32,"Abo bangakholwayo bathi: “Kutheni na i’Kur’ân ingatyhilwayo kuye yonke ngaxeshalinye?” (oko kunjalo) khon’ukuze Someleze intliziyo yakho ngayo (Muhammad) yaye Siyityhile kuwe iziziqendu ngeziqendu"
  25,33,Akukho mzekelo okanye umzekeliso abeza nawo kuwe Singakuziseli nyaniso nengcaciso epheleleyo (ngawo)
  25,34,Abo baza kuqokelelwa ngobuso babo basiwe esiHogweni abo ngabona bakwimo emaxongo ngakumbi yaye balahleke kakhulu eNdleleni
  25,35,Kananjalo Sanika uMûsâ isiBhalo Samnyulela umntakwabo uHârûn ukuba abe ngumncedisi wakhe
  25,36,"Sathi (kubo): “Hambani nobabini niye kubantu abaphike imiqondiso yeThu.” Saza Sabatshabalalisa ngentshabalalo ebhubhisayo"
  25,37,"Nabantu bakwaNûh, ukuphika kwabo abaThunywa, Sabatshonisa emanzini, Sabenza umzekelo eluntwini. Yaye Silungiselele abenzi bobubi isohlwayo esibuhlungu"
  25,38,"Kanti nabakwa’Ad nabakwaThamûd, nabanini bequla nezizukulwana ezininzi phakathi kwabo"
  25,39,"Kananjalo (kwisizukulwana) ngasinye Senza imizekelo (ukuba ibe zizilumkiso), yaye ngasinye kuzo Sasitshabalisa (safa) nya"
  25,40,Ke kaloku babesele begqithagqithile ngakwidolophu (yoMprofeti uLût) ekwathululwa phezu kwayo imvula engcolileyo4. Ingaba abangakholwayo babengaboni na? Yeha kubo! Kaloku babengalindelanga luvuko
  25,41,"Ke kaloku xa bekubona wena (Muhammad) bakuthabatha njengento yokuhlekisa (besithi): “Ingaba lo ngulowo uAllâh amthumele njengoMthunywa"
  25,42,"Ebeza kuphantsela ukusilahlekisa koothixo bethu, ukuba ngaba ibingeyiyo into yokuba sinomonde sithe rhoqo (ukubakhonza).” Kodwa baza kwazi xa bebona isohlwayo, ukuba ngubani na olahleke kakhulu eNdleleni"
  25,43,Ingaba umbonile na lowo uzithabathele iminqweno yakhe ukuba ibe nguthixo wakhe? Ungaze ube nguye umnoneleli wakhe wena
  25,44,"Okanye ucinga okokuba uninzi lwabo luyeva okanye luyaqiqa? Bona banjengeenkomo yeha, bona balahleke nangakumbi (kuneenkomo) eNdleleni"
  25,45,"Ingaba ubonile na ukuba iNkosi yakho Isolule njani na isithunzi. Ukuba Ibithanda, Ibingasuka isenze sime ngxishi Kodwa Senze ilanga laba ngumkhokeli waso"
  25,46,Size Silibambe kuThi ngokubamba okulula
  25,47,"Kananjalo nguYe Onenzela ubusuku bube sisigqumathelo, nokulala ibe kukuphumla Aze Enze imini ibe kukuvuka (kwenu)"
  25,48,"NguYe Othumela imimoya ibe zizanduleli zeendaba ezilungileyo, ihamba phambi kwenceba yaKhe (imvula); yaye Sithoba amanzi ahlambulukileyo esuka esibhakabhakeni"
  25,49,"Khon’ukuze ngawo Sinike ubomi emhlabeni ofileyo, Size Sinike iinkomo nabantu abaninzi eSabadalayo basele kuwo"
  25,50,"Kananjalo inene Thina Siwachakachakile (amanzi emvula) phakathi kwabo khon’ukuze bakhumbuzeke, kodwa abaninzi kubo akukho nto bayamkelayo ngaphandle kokungakholwa"
  25,51,Kanti ke ukuba SaSithandile ngeSathumela uMlumkisi5 kwidolophu nganye
  25,52,"Ngoko ke ungabathobeli abangakholwayo, zabalaza kananjalo ngokuchasene nabo ngayo (i’Kur’ân), ibe ngumzabalazo omkhulu"